*PrimaryInterface: sanctuary
EventCustomColumns:
Site: : Sampled at Sepilok Orangutan Sanctuary, Batu 14, Jalan Labuk Sandakan Sabah WDT200, 9009 Sandakan Sabah (N 5.8652, E 117.9489)
Event: : Sampling of a dead proboscis monkey with EHA and Sabah Wildlife Rescue Unit (WRU)
Source: : Proboscis monkey found dead at Lot 6, Lower Kinabatangan Wildlife Sanctuary, Sabah, Malaysia.
FieldNecropsyResults: Post-mortem result: The animal may fight with other animal or injured by the predator. The neckbone was nearly broken, bites found at both  sides of waist area, no internal hemorrhagic
sampleUnitNotes: The animal was found sitting on the ground in the forest and it was dead after 1-2 hour(s). The carcass was collected by reserchers based in Danau Girang Field Centre, Sandakan , Sabah.
sampleUnitCustomColumns: Animal ID assigned by other organization: WRU & DGFC- KIN18
